Dion Wired is running an awesome tech sale from 8-21 May 2019, where customers can save thousands of rands on the latest electronics and gadgets from brands like Samsung, LG, Apple, and more. Included in the sale are the latest Samsung QLED and LG OLED TVs, with sizes ranging from 55-inch all the way up to 75-inch. PlayStation and Xbox gaming consoles, laptops, soundbars, smartphones, cameras, printers, tablets, and headphones are also available at big discounts – along with a range of the latest fridges and kitchen appliances. To see all the great deals, visit Dion Wired’s website. A selection of the best tech and gadget deals from the Dion Wired sale are shown below. <img class="size-full wp-image-306250 aligncenter" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/LG-65-INCH-TV.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/LG-65-INCH-TV.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/LG-65-INCH-TV-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/LG-65-INCH-TV-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="size-full wp-image-306248 aligncenter" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/iPad-Air.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/iPad-Air.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/iPad-Air-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/iPad-Air-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="size-full wp-image-306240 aligncenter" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/ASUS-Zenbook.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/ASUS-Z